ECB’s Costa Says Portugal’s Financial Industry Is ‘Solid’

-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 
2011-09-28T10:41:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/ecb-s-costa-says-portugal-s-financial-industry-is-solid-.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Carlos Costa said markets need to recognize that
 Portugal ’s financial sector is “solid.”  “One of the most relevant factors we need to point out is
that the financial system is solid and has the confidence of
bank clients,” he said in Lisbon today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
